name: Stormy Fortress
description:
Appearances can be deceiving. Although this building looks like a castle, it is actually a 19th century army barracks located in Hungary. I explored and photographed this location in the winter of 2019. I created this piece to celebrate HEN 500k, and all the artists forming this wonderful community. Here is to another 500 OBJKTS!

Mp4 | 1080x1080 pixels| Nov  2021
